data.description: Charming One-Level Home with Ample Space and Privacy?This lovely home sits on just over half an acre of land and offers plenty of space to relax and unwind. Conveniently located near local shopping, dining, and Rte. 29, this property boasts excellent parking and a spacious backyard for your enjoyment. You'll also find additional storage space in the large 12x28 building on the premises. The home has been recently updated with an array of features, including newer windows, doors, siding, roof, HVAC, and gutters, as well as 50-amp generator wiring. As you enter the home, you'll be greeted by a welcoming entrance and a cozy living room that flows seamlessly into the eat-in kitchen. A large laundry closet and pantry provide ample storage space. The home offers three bedrooms and one-and-a-half bathrooms, with recent updates to the bathrooms. Step outside onto the wonderful large deck, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying a quiet night under the stars.
